rong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>∙</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>∙</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>&nbsp;(hence&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>L</mi></math> and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>M</mi></math> are parallel to the plane)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>6</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>×</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>4</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>20</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>10</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mfenced><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;(hence&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>L</mi></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>M</mi></math>&nbsp;are parallel to the plan